+### Error handling strategy
+
+Fail fast on usage errors (throw → `Error: …`, exit 1). Diagnosis never
+throws for in-scope degradation — degradation becomes findings; only
+environment failures (unreadable workflow dir, IO errors other than
+NotFound) propagate. Repair is transactional per artifact: backup is
+written before the tmp+rename swap; refusal paths return before any
+write.
